Q3. Matrix Multiplication: Write a program to display multiplication of two matrices entered by the user?
Input:
int[][] A = {
    {2, 4, 1, 3},
    {1, 2, 0, 1}
};
int[][] B = {
    {1, 2, 3},
    {0, 1, 4},
    {2, 3, 1},
    {1, 0, 2}
};
Note:- isme addition of matix ke jaisa restriction nhi hota but isme phla matix ke number of columns , dusre matrix ke number of rows ke equals hona chahiye. or final jo mutliplication
       jo hogi wo phle martrix ke rows and dusre matrix ke columns ke equals.
       also first matrix ke column ke hr - ek element and second matrix ke hr-ek row ke element ko pick krne ke liye ek loop or lgega wo 0 to first array ke column ke length ya second aaray
       ke row ke length ke equals chlega.



